comments: Aldridge (BKN) firms up in his screening position in Wade's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact.
Wade (CLE) moves alongside Durant's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Durant's drive.
Aldridge (BKN) and Allen (CLE) come together at the same shot following the release of the shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs as Aldridge establishes rebounding position.
Aldridge (BKN) makes contact with the ball after it bounces out of the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Durant (BKN) engages and disengages with Allen (CLE) as Allen moves to set the pick.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (BKN) path and absorbs the contact. Allen and Harden engage and disengage with one another as Allen rolls toward the lane.
Durant (BKN) retrieves the ball as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Allen's (CLE) back during rebounding.
Wade (CLE) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another as they move over the screen.
Aldridge (BKN) firms up in his screening position in Wade's (CLE) path and absorbs the side-to-side contact.
Durant (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Okoro's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact.
Wade (CLE) moves forward toward Harden (BKN) and marginal body contact occurs as Harden moves around the pick.
Rubio (CLE) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Aldridge (BKN) and Garland (CLE) engage and disengage with one another as the screen is set during the inbound.
Johnson's (BKN) left arm is extended to the side and marginal contact occurs with Wade's (CLE) front and right arm as Johnson retrieves the rebound.
Johnson (BKN) moves toward Rubio (CLE) in transition and marginal contact occurs as Johnson's off-arm releases away from Rubio's front.
Markkanen (CLE) makes contact to Johnson's (BKN) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Wade (CLE) maintains a rested forearm on Aldridge's (BKN) left side and marginal contact occurs as Aldridge attempts the put-back.
Wade (CLE) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Aldridge (BKN) before any incidental contact occurs.
Allen (CLE) grasps and then quickly releases Harden's (BKN) left arm as the pass into the post is made.
Harden (BKN) pulls Allen's (CLE) jersey away from his body and affects his FOM as the post entry pass is made.
Harden (BKN) grasps and then quickly releases Markkanen's (CLE) jersey as the screen is set during the inbound.
Harden (BKN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Mills (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position as body contact occurs with Garland's (CLE) back/side during the drive.
Garland (CLE) commits a take foul on Mills (BKN).
Durant (BKN) extends both hands into Rubio's (CLE) front and dislodges Rubio from his position during the inbound.
Mills (BKN) and Garland (CLE) engage and disengage with one another as they move over the screen.
Allen (CLE) firms up in his screening position in Mills' (BKN) path and absorbs the contact.
Johnson (BKN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Wade (CLE) before any incidental arm contact occurs.
Johnson (BKN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Johnson (BKN) extends his hand into Markkanen's (CLE) side and initiates contact that affects Markkanen's shot attempt near the rim.
Rubio (CLE) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Allen (CLE) brushes Harden's (BKN) left arm and marginal contact occurs as Markkanen (CLE) simultaneously makes clean contact with the ball.
Markkanen's (CLE) feet are out of bounds when he makes contact with the ball.
Wade (CLE) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Wade (CLE) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
